                    <note type="corrigenda">In Dolabani's translation of Barsoum's description <quote xml:lang="syr-Syrj">ܘܐܰܦܩ</quote> and <quote xml:lang="syr-Syrj">ܡܟܰܬܒܰܙܰܒܢܗ</quote> 
                        should read <quote xml:lang="syr-Syrj">ܘܰܐܦܩ</quote> and <quote xml:lang="syr-Syrj">ܡܰܟܬܰܒܙܰܒܢܗ</quote> respectively.</note>
                    <note type="corrigenda">Matti Moosa's English translation of Barsoum's description is incomplete, and it says "north" when it should be "east."</note>
